{"tid":1674583,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【東體爭議】曼聯最需要球員喺阿仙奴雪櫃","createTime":"2019-10-25T09:41:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T17:57:01.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"89876954885b34ad1d90604652a1017508c4db8f","tid":1674583,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:41:13.000Z","msg":"曾被摩連奴譽為球壇「最佳10號」嘅奧斯爾，周五(25號)歐霸盃再一次無緣入選阿仙奴大軍名單，亦係佢連續第5場喺冇傷冇病情況之下，連18人名單都入唔到，顯而易見嘅係，阿仙奴已經完全將佢踢出計劃之內。<br />\n奧斯爾嘅優點同弱點分明，用唔用佢亦引嚟唔少爭論，不過曼聯名宿史高斯就話，奧斯爾正正就係曼聯依家最需要嘅球員。史高斯為BT Sport評述歐霸盃嗰陣，同拍擋討論奧斯爾嘅情況時表示：「我唔明白(奧斯爾被棄用)，我認為奧斯爾係可以連繫全隊嘅球員，佢有好高質素嘅技術，呢一點佢嘅足球生涯已經證明咗，我唔知道，但佢可以成為曼聯短期『答案』。如果奧斯爾肯減薪嘅話係有可能，我唔覺得呢件事(轉會曼聯)會發生，但奧斯爾呢類型球員，係曼聯依家最需要嘅球員。」"},{"pid":"c6952ac141c98fcf73401573001246428ec1f3f9","tid":1674583,"uid":199590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"曼=阿仙奴垃圾桶"},{"pid":"1ab43a2447e73e5ca9eae9020d5fe6a4c1d312a8","tid":1674583,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6952ac141c98fcf73401573001246428ec1f3f9","tid":1674583,"uid":199590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"曼=阿仙奴垃圾桶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:49:53.000Z","msg":"尊重"},{"pid":"fc08e55838c157b78811eb90550c0cc07907f35d","tid":1674583,"uid":9951,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3nYVdT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3nYVdT.jpg&h=0d4dfe10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25ed721d108f3da393e855fd6633ee008c9a3f81","tid":1674583,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc08e55838c157b78811eb90550c0cc07907f35d","tid":1674583,"uid":9951,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3nYVdT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3nYVdT.jpg&h=0d4dfe10&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:45:16.000Z","msg":"我都唔明點解當初唔要奧燒要佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77679d22d0cdda4f3722ec1e911ace61d8dd2c86","tid":1674583,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"有無成日打開雪櫃搞到凍親篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9eeeb432c32ef7cc5bdbc8be72d3aca4186f08","tid":1674583,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e9vztW4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe9vztW4.gif&h=8b1249aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c486f9602ef4e42f3a7f25dfc3488c6d479f6694","tid":1674583,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}